tuv.seg: Magnus Thue lea máhttoministara Torbjørn Røe Isaksen politihkalaš ráđđeaddi.
Magnus Thue is Political Advisor to the Minister of Education and Research Torbjørn Røe Isaksen.
Bjørn Haugstad nammaduvvui máhttoministara Torbjørn Røe Isaksen stáhtačállin golggotmánu 16. b. 2013.
Bjørn Haugstad was appointed State Secretary to the Minister of Education and Research Torbjørn Røe Isaksen on 16 October 2013.
